trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection" /> class contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: La classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection" /> contiene una raccolta di oggetti <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> object to locate.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> da individuare.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection.Contains(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference)" /> method determines if the collection contains specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Il metodo <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection.Contains(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference)" /> determina se l'insieme contiene l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> specificato.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the collection contains <paramref name="value" /> or <see langword="false" /> if it does not.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se l'insieme contiene <paramref name="value" />; in caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: A one-dimensional array that is the destination of the elements copied from the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Matrice unidimensionale che costituisce la destinazione degli elementi copiati dall'oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of <c>values</c> where copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Indice in base zero di <c>values</c> in cui ha inizio la copia.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection.CopyTo(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference[],System.Int32)" /> method copies the entire collection to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Il metodo <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection.CopyTo(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference[],System.Int32)" /> copia l'intero insieme in una matrice unidimensionale, a partire dall'indice specificato della matrice di destinazione.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="values" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="values" /> è un riferimento null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> è minore di zero.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="values" /> is multidimensional
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="values" /> è multidimensionale

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: oppure

trans-unit.source: The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection" /> is greater than the available space from <paramref name="index" /> to the end of the destination <paramref name="values" />.
trans-unit.target: Il numero di elementi nell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection" /> di origine è maggiore dello spazio disponibile tra <paramref name="index" /> e la fine dell'oggetto <paramref name="values" /> di destinazione.

trans-unit.source: The type of the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection" /> cannot be cast automatically to the type of the destination <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: Non è possibile eseguire il cast automatico del tipo dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection" /> di origine al tipo dell'oggetto <paramref name="array" /> di destinazione.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> object for which the index is returned.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> per il quale viene restituito l'indice.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection.IndexOf(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference)" /> method returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> object in <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Il metodo <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection.IndexOf(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference)" /> restituisce l'indice in base zero della prima occorrenza dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> specificato in <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The index value of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> object, if found.
trans-unit.target: Valore di indice dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> specificato, se presente.

trans-unit.source: If the object is not found, this method returns -1.
trans-unit.target: Se l'oggetto non è presente, il metodo restituisce -1.

trans-unit.source: The index value of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Valore di indice dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection.Item(System.Int32)" /> property contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> object at the specified <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: La proprietà <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReferenceCollection.Item(System.Int32)" /> contiene l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> in corrispondenza dell'oggetto <paramref name="index" /> specificato.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> object at the specified <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> in corrispondenza dell'oggetto <paramref name="index" /> specificato.
